Original

image1 <- readPNG("image1.png")[,,1]
image2 <- readPNG("image2.png")[,,1]
grid.newpage()
grid.raster(image1)

grid.newpage()
grid.raster(image2)

Adaptive thresholding

grid.newpage()
par(mfrow=c(1,2))
ada1 <- ada_threshold(data = image1)
# writePNG(ada1, "ada_image1.png")
ada2 <- ada_threshold(data = image2)
# writePNG(ada2, "ada_image2.png")
grid.newpage()
grid.raster(ada1)

grid.newpage()
grid.raster(ada2)
